地对小鸡说：一天一个蛋，菜刀靠边站，一月不生蛋，高压锅里见。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">　　存在是因为你创造价值，淘汰是因为你失去价值。过去的价值不代表未来，所以每天都要努力！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">02</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　张三在山间小路开车，正当他悠哉欣赏美丽风景时，突然迎面开来的货车司机摇下窗户大喊一声：“猪！”张三越想越气，也摇下车窗大骂：“你才是猪！”刚骂完，他便迎头撞上一群过马路的猪。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">　　不要错误地诠释别人的好意，那只会让自己吃亏，并且使别人受辱。在不明所以之前，先学会按捺情绪，耐心观察，以免事后生发悔意。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">03</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　丈夫下班回到家，看见妻子揍儿子，没理他们。径直走到厨房，看见小矮桌上煮好一锅馄饨，于是盛了一碗吃。吃完看见妻子还在那里揍儿子，看不过去了，就说：“教育小孩不能老用暴力，要多讲道理嘛！”妻子说：“好好的一锅馄饨，他居然撒了一泡尿进去，你说气人不气人？”丈夫听后马上说：“媳妇你歇会儿，让我来揍！&nbsp;”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">　　置身事外，谁都可以心平气和；身处其中，谁还可以从容淡定。所以请不要轻易评论任何人，因为你不在其中……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">04</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">乞丐：“能不能给我一百块钱？”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">路人：“我只有八十块钱。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">乞丐：“那你就欠我二十块钱吧。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">　　有些人总以为是上苍欠他的，老觉得老天爷给的不够多、不够好，贪婪之欲早已取代了感恩之心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px;\">05</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">　　一滴墨汁落在一杯清水里，这杯水立即变色，不能喝了；一滴墨汁融在大海里，大海依然是蔚蓝色的大海。为什么？因为两者的肚量不一样！不熟的麦穗直刺刺地向上挺着，成熟的麦穗低垂着头。为什么？因为两者的份量不一样！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; background: white; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\">　　宽容别人，就是肚量；谦卑自己，就是份量；合起来，就是一个人的质量。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">上面五个小故事给我自己的感悟就是：人要活到老学到老，永远不要停止加强自我学习和自身修为，不断丰富自己的精神内涵，老老实实做人，踏踏实实做事，感恩同事陪伴，感谢领导关怀，珍惜单位、企业给予自己的工作机会和施展才能的工作平台，立足本职岗位，干好本职工作。</span></p><p><br/></p>','',200,1,'',1,'','',1541471905,50,0,'','',0,0,'1',0,1,0,'{\"showdate\":1541433600}','zh-cn'),(124,'请善待单位里的老实人','',18,NULL,'','','1','管理员','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不知从什么时候开始，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“老实”</strong>一词不再指诚实、忠厚、规矩，而成了痴笨、窝囊、无能的代名词，说谁老实那就是在骂人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">但如果说谁<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">“老练”</strong>，则可能被认为是一种夸赞。这种认知，代表了一种作风、一种价值取向。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">华而不实，怨之所聚也。”如果让华而不实的“老练”之风盛行，必然为祸不浅；反过来，多一些老实少一些“老练”，才能风清气正。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">老实是立身从政之本，不可稍废；“老练”是侥幸行险之举，不可追捧。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">请善待并重用这10种老实人！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">01</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不和领导套近乎又能积极配合领导工作的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不套近乎，工作任劳任怨，服从命令，这类老实人注重的是主动干事，不习惯于察言观色，一切听从组织安排。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">相反，一些人也“积极”配合领导工作，但是夹杂个人私利，见风使舵，投其所好。这种积极配合，本质就是实现个人目的，最容易让领导“眼花缭乱”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">02</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不和领导多走动又能体谅领导良苦用心的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">这类老实人，工作中有了一点点成长进步、生活上得到一丝丝照顾，都能够深切体谅到组织、领导的关心和厚爱，以更高标准、更好状态投入工作，用实绩来报答组织的关爱，而不是靠多和领导走动来获取什么。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">03</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不经常往领导家里跑常常往基层跑的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">他们把心思和精力都放在了基层，不怕领导注不注意，就怕基层满不满意。他们想得更多的是基层疾苦和群众困难，他们能记住老百姓的门朝东还是朝西开，却记不住领导家的门牌号码。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">如果领导不常下基层，就不知他们姓甚名谁，他们最容易被忽视和埋没，也最容易吃亏。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">04</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不关心领导生活私事却帮群众排忧解难的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">这类老实人，不琢磨人，专琢磨事。他们对领导的生活习性、兴趣爱好知之不多，对老百姓的需求、困难很是上心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">对有些领导来说，他们往往容易被看作不会来事、不懂“道理”，太木讷、不机灵。但实际上，这才是干事的人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">05</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不当面恭维领导但能自觉树立领导威信的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">他们不习惯于说客套话，不会拍领导的马屁。在他们心中，威信不是说出来的，而是靠工作、业绩立起来的。只有老老实实做人，扎扎实实干事，才能受人尊敬和爱戴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">同事对工作安排有怨气，他们积极开导。领导部署中出现疏漏，他们私下委婉提出，补台而不拆台。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">06</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不向领导表态但能高标准完成工作任务的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">他们有一个重要特征，就是不声不响地干，竭尽全力地干，低调做人、高调做事。这里的高调，不是空喊口号，而是对工作任劳任怨，一丝不苟，尽最大努力去完成。他们认为“干得好”比“说得好”更能体现人生价值。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">07</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不爱多邀功多表功但能创造性工作的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">这些人把所有心思凝聚在工作上，为了干好工作他们走千山万水，说千言万语，吃千辛万苦，想千方百计。可是，他们对自己的功劳只字不提。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">这样的老实人，不加以关注和重视，时间一长就会挫伤他们的积极性和创造性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">08</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不爱向组织提个人要求但又积极表现的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">他们表现、业绩都很突出，为了工作甚至可以受常人难以忍受的委屈和痛苦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;然而，他们在个人进步面前，往往难以启齿，不好意思开口。领导一定要主动关心这类人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">09</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 20px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">不爱看领导脸色行事又能公事公办的人。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">他们坚持原则，不徇私情，最能保护人，也最容易得罪人。他们不看领导脸色行事，只依规章制度办事。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">其实，领导干部应以拥有这种老实人而自豪，因为他们是领导的“保护神”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", \"Lucida Grande\", Tahoma, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", STHeiti, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: Arial; background: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体, arial, sans-serif, \"DejaVu Sans\", 