 none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:   12px;font-family:宋体\">田书勇</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"70\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:   12px;font-family:宋体\">张伟</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"179\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><p style=\"line-height:16px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">完成公司所有视频监控系统整合规范使用方案</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"73\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:16px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">生技部</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"76\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><br/></td><td width=\"50\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">11</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:12px;font-family:宋体\">月30日</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"58\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent:13px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:7px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">二、会议要求：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">HSE</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）生技部、客户中心负责，严格监控大智无疆公司用气，及时收费；经发部要每周对绿地双子塔项目进度进行跟踪。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）安监部牵头，输配站配合，做好“</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">11.9</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">消防演练”相关准备工作。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（三）相关单位（部室）要以此次西分司</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">QHSE</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">体系审核为契机，清理完善相关资料台账。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（四）管道部牵头、生技部配合，清理公司与其他单位临时运行的天然气管线；制定相应应急预案，并开展演练。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">经营管理类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）经发部牵头，尽快完成大修项目控制价的编制以及金融大道结算资料审查。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）各相关单位（部室）要加快“三供一业”改造进度，务必在年底完成。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">生产运行类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）客户中心要对抄表工作开展不定期抽查，提高抄表工作的完成率、准确率。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）客户中心要认真了解</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年未能安装的</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">148</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">户具体原因、目前现状，要创造条件，力争安装到位。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（三）张剑副经理负责，尽快完成管道标识桩、标识块的补充安装工作。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（四）生技部牵头，客户中心配合，对收费大厅及其他两处收费点视频盲区，拿出整改方案，并加装摄像头。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">党建类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年即将结束，且当下各单位（部室）出差人员较多，各单位（部室）负责要确实担负起责任，要认真梳理、安排好各路工作，圆满完成全年任务。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）各单位（部室）进一步按机关作风建设要求，加强组织纪律及工作作风管理。</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";position:absolute;z-index:2;left:0px;margin-top:41px;width:590px;height:2px\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"2\" src=\"http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:/Users/wy/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtml1/01/clip_image001.gif\" style=\"background:url(http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span><span style=\";position:relative;z-index:1\"><span style=\"left:0px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;width:590px;height:2px\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"2\" src=\"http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:/Users/wy/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtml1/01/clip_image001.gif\" style=\"background:url(http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">中油南充燃气有限责任公司办公室</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;2018<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月</span>5<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">日</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">印发</span></p><p><br/></p>','',200,1,'',1,'','',1541578419,50,0,'','',0,0,'1',0,1,0,'{\"showdate\":1541520000}','zh-cn');
INSERT INTO `yf_news` VALUES (186,'（第63期）周一安全生产经营碰头会纪要','',32,NULL,'','','1','管理员','<p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:150%;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">第( 63 )期</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;line-height:150%;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">中油南充燃气有限责任公司&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2018-11-05</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:29px;font-family:方正小标宋简体\">周一安全生产经营碰头会纪要</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:29px;font-family:黑体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">时</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">间：</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">日</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">地</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">点：三楼会议室</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">主</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">持：田书勇</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:85px\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">参加人：王</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">睿、文</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">晓、代</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">进、陈</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">敏、张</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">剑、郭</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">兵、任</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">敏、饶</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">贵、张</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">伟、李光照、廖</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">莎、吴兴元、李静波、鞠</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">英、唐</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">勇、陈</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">飞、胡晓霖、叶文华、汪晓梅、胡</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">浩、林</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">敏、郑</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\"> &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">鹏</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;line-height:43px\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">会上，恩阳分公司作了《恩阳区玉山镇胜利街杨柏春“</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">9.1</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">”燃气事故》安全经验分享以及《请善待单位里的老实人》的正能量分享；客户中心汇报了</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年供气项目分期收款情况、居民用气新申请情况及户表改造情况；生技部汇报</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年城镇燃气工程相关情况；安监部通报了全国</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月份燃气安全事故，汇报了</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月份公司安全隐患监督检查及稽核稽查情况；代进副经理传达了南充“三供一业”相关会议精神，对公司改造价格进行了通报；文晓书记传达了南充市环保相关会议精神，对公司现场施工、配气站的环保情况进行了要求，对</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">12340</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">党风廉政热线接听进行了要求；王睿经理组织学习了《川港燃气公司三季度安全生产经营分析会》精神，对川港燃气公司总经理王天彪的要求进行了传达；公司各单位（部室）对上周工作进行了总结，对本周工作进行了安排；公司领导对近期及下一步工作进行了布置：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">一、近期工作部署：</span></p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"623\"><tbody><tr style=\";height:36px\" class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"29\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"36\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">序号</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"62\" style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"36\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">指令人</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"70\" style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"36\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">牵头人</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"179\" style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-top-color: windowtext; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"36\"><p style=\"text-align:center;background:white\"><strong><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">主要工作内容</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"73\" style=\"border-top-width: 1px; border-rig