"58\" style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1px; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0px 7px;\" height=\"53\"><br/></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-indent:13px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:7px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">二、会议要求：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">HSE</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）生技部、客户中心负责，严格监控大智无疆公司用气，及时收费；经发部要每周对绿地双子塔项目进度进行跟踪。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）安监部牵头，输配站配合，做好“</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">11.9</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">消防演练”相关准备工作。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（三）相关单位（部室）要以此次西分司</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">QHSE</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">体系审核为契机，清理完善相关资料台账。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（四）管道部牵头、生技部配合，清理公司与其他单位临时运行的天然气管线；制定相应应急预案，并开展演练。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">经营管理类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）经发部牵头，尽快完成大修项目控制价的编制以及金融大道结算资料审查。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）各相关单位（部室）要加快“三供一业”改造进度，务必在年底完成。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">生产运行类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）客户中心要对抄表工作开展不定期抽查，提高抄表工作的完成率、准确率。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）客户中心要认真了解</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年未能安装的</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">148</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">户具体原因、目前现状，要创造条件，力争安装到位。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（三）张剑副经理负责，尽快完成管道标识桩、标识块的补充安装工作。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（四）生技部牵头，客户中心配合，对收费大厅及其他两处收费点视频盲区，拿出整改方案，并加装摄像头。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体简体\">党建类</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（一）</span><span style=\"font-size:21px\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年即将结束，且当下各单位（部室）出差人员较多，各单位（部室）负责要确实担负起责任，要认真梳理、安排好各路工作，圆满完成全年任务。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">（二）各单位（部室）进一步按机关作风建设要求，加强组织纪律及工作作风管理。</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:43px;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";position:absolute;z-index:2;left:0px;margin-top:41px;width:590px;height:2px\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"2\" src=\"http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:/Users/wy/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtml1/01/clip_image001.gif\" style=\"background:url(http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span><span style=\";position:relative;z-index:1\"><span style=\"left:0px;position:absolute;left:-1px;top:-1px;width:590px;height:2px\"><img width=\"590\" height=\"2\" src=\"http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///C:/Users/wy/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtml1/01/clip_image001.gif\" style=\"background:url(http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd\"/></span></span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">中油南充燃气有限责任公司办公室</span><span style=\"font-size:19px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;2018<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">年</span>11<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">月</span>5<span style=\"font-family:方正仿宋简体\">日</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:方正仿宋简体\">印发</span></p><p><br/></p>','',200,0,'',1,'','',1541578421,50,0,'','',0,1,'0',0,1,0,'{\"showdate\":1541520000}','zh-cn'),(187,'西油公司安全管理制度','',65,NULL,'','','1','管理员','<p style=\"line-height: 16px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;\" src=\"http://10.89.219.127/public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_rar.gif\"/><a style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;\" hr